{"tid":1657881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國台辦斥台灣民進黨有關部門將香港警察誣衊為｢黑警」","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T09:45:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0bd00d55517ba3cc495c4116a593ef6a2f30ea","tid":1657881,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"在北京，國台辦批評，台灣民進黨有關部門負責人，將香港警察誣衊為｢黑警｣，説明心中只有黨派利益，全無法律正義。<br />\n<br />\n發言人馬曉光說，事實證明台灣網上傳播所謂香港警察逃往或移居台灣，是不折不扣的假消息，對於違反基本常識的假消息，民進黨有關部門負責人如獲至寶，在網站上大肆炒作，結果使自己淪為政治笑話，將維護法律秩序、維護人民生命財產安全的執法者誣衊為｢黑警｣。<br />\n<br />\n馬曉光認為，事件與民進黨利用個人權位公然庇護｢私煙案｣、｢高鐵失落現金案｣等弊案的行為如出一轍，誰黑誰白一目了然。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的内政部移民署日前在社交網站貼文，指接到網上消息，大批香港｢黑警｣將帶同家眷申請移民台灣，當局將嚴謹把關移民審核，將不法及犯罪阻絕於境外。"},{"pid":"e91cee13b703cc0985799c673614ba389d32f143","tid":1657881,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"邊有誣衊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2caa77c94f7675af5c51638599ae0b1e4e33ad","tid":1657881,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c21c0c290c858f799eb72e0b38e3beae6ac51876","tid":1657881,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df2caa77c94f7675af5c51638599ae0b1e4e33ad","tid":1657881,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:45:06.